fg_segments: All Acronyms Privacy PolicyAll Acronyms values the users of our web site (the "Web Site") and the services offered on it (the "All Acronyms Services").

We recognize that you may be concerned about our collection, use, and disclosure of your personally identifiable information ("Personal Information") that we may collect when you use the Web Site and the All Acronyms Services.

Your privacy is very important to us. Accordingly, we have implemented this Privacy Policy to inform you of the information that we collect from you, how we collect this information, and what we do with it after we collect it.
By using the All Acronyms Web Site you are accepting the practices described in this policy.

Cookies and Web Beacons All Acronyms may use cookies, web beacons, or similar technologies to enhance and personalize your experience on All Acronyms website, including to operate and improve offerings through the All Acronyms; to help authenticate your identity when you visit and transact with All Acronyms; to remember your preferences and registration information; enable a shopping cart; to present and help measure and research the effectiveness of All Acronyms offerings, advertisements, and e-mail communications (by determining which All Acronyms e-mails you open and act upon); and to customize the content and advertisements provide to you by All Acronyms.
Additionally, All Acronyms or its advertisers may use other companies known as third party ad servers to help present advertisements online in connection with All Acronyms Products.
These third party ad servers may use cookies, web beacons, or similar technologies to help present such advertisements, and to help measure and research the advertisements' effectiveness.
The use of these technologies by these third party ad servers is subject to their own privacy policies, not All Acronyms's.
Changes to this Privacy Policy and Additional Information The All Acronyms Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time, and so you should review this Policy periodically.
